TextEng: Hello, I am <FullName>. Could I ask some questions?
Text: 안녕하세요, 저는 <FullName>입니다. 몇 가지 여쭤봐도 될까요?

TextEng: I'm <FullName>. I have some questions.
Text: 난 <FullName>. 몇 가지 물어볼 게 있어요.

TextEng: I'm <FullName>. Just shut up and answer my questions.
Text: 난 <FullName>. 입 닥치고 내 질문에나 답해요.

TextEng: Me <FullName>. Maybe me ask you some things?
Me <FullName>. You just shuts up and answer questions, okay?
Text: 나 <FullName>. 입 다물고 질문에 답해, 알겠지?

TextEng: Farewell, then.
Bye bye.
What is your position here?
What your job here?
Is there a place for nature in the heart of this city?
Text: 이 도시 한복판에도 자연이 설 자리가 있습니까?

TextEng: Nature in the city? Wha?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Why are you so sure this plague is not natural?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 왜 이 역병이 자연스러운 현상이 아니라고 확신하죠?

TextEng: Me needs stuff to buy. What you gots?
I require supplies. What can you offer?
Text: 보급품이 필요합니다. 무엇을 주실 수 있죠?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe me can still help?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I might still be able to help.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 혹시 도움이 될 수 있을지도 모르겠습니다.

TextEng: It can't be new. Not during the plague.
Text: 역병이 도는 지금, 새로 생긴 일은 아니겠군요.

TextEng: Can't be new. Not during plague-sick.
Text: 새로 생긴 건 아니겠네. 역병 도는 판에.

TextEng: This zoo seems small next to the plague.
Text: 역병에 비하면 동물원은 사소한 문제 같은데요.

TextEng: So animals are in a zoo. So what?
I will help you free these animals.
This bad! Me free animals!
I have no interest in helping.
Me no want to bother with this.
What do you know of this hunter?
Text: 그 사냥꾼에 대해 뭘 알고 계십니까?

TextEng: Who this hunter guy?
No! Me demands more!
Me not care about this.
Go over what is needed again.
Text: 필요한 게 뭔지 다시 설명해 줘.

TextEng: You repeat stuff about this job, okay?
Text: 이 일에 대해 다시 말해줘, 응?

TextEng: Go over the task with me. Perhaps I will help too.
Text: 할 일을 다시 설명해 주십시오. 저도 도울 수 있을지 모르니까요.

TextEng: You tell me stuff too. Maybe me help.
Text: 내용 알려줘. 나 도울 수도 있어.

TextEng: There some stuff done about animals!
There has been progress in freeing the animals.
I will help.
Me help!
I have no interest in this.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You must agree that I am worth more.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 제가 더 받을 만하다는 거 인정하시죠.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You knows me worth more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 그거보다 더 받을 만한 거 알잖아.

TextEng: I demand more! Deny me and you will suffer!
Text: 더 내라! 거절하면 대가를 치르게 될 것이다!

TextEng: Me wants more, or me hurt you bad!
Text: 더 줘, 아니면 혼쭐 낼 거야!

TextEng: That is sufficient. Thank you.
That really good. Thanks for the stuff.
That will not do! I demand more!
Farewell
Bye bye
What is the purpose of the zoo?
Why they cage animals?
I need the key.
Me need key.
I need the scroll.
Me need scroll.
Nothing more. Goodbye.
Perhaps more for a <brother/sister> druid?
Text: 동료 드루이드에게는 좀 더 줘야 하지 않을까?

TextEng: What animals? Is there something you need help with?
Text: 무슨 동물이요? 도움이 필요한 일이 있습니까?

TextEng: What animals? Maybe you need help or something?
